    Getting started with the oneimpact package in R

Cabins vector data

Source: R/data.R
cabins_vect.gpkg.Rd

Dataset containing the location of tourist private cabins is Southern Norway, within the study area for the oneimpact package. It corresponds to some specific building types (object_type = "Bygning", byggtyp_nbr = c("161", "162", "163")) form the public N50 dataset. The map was cut for the study area presented in the oneimpact package.

Format

A geopackage file. Projected CRS: ETRS89 / UTM zone 33N. The vector file presents the following columns:

  • cat: Line number, corresponding to the original dataset

  • byggtyp_nbr: Type of building (code) in the original dataset

  • kommune: Code of the municipality where the cabin is located

  • value: Value 1, to be used for rasterization purposes

Source

https://register.geonorge.no/det-offentlige-kartgrunnlaget/n50-kartdata/ea192681-d039-42ec-b1bc-f3ce04c189ac
